 stochastic\nheating. The observed SED of Cas A SNR is reasonably reproduced by the model of\ndust formation and evolution for Type IIb SN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Mar 2009 07:02:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Mar 2009 22:55:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-05"}
