ransition line. The\nthermodynamic stability of the phases is investigated by a careful analysis of\nthe Hessian matrix of the free energy. We show that all principal minors of the\nHessian are positive in the limit of zero replicas, implying in particular that\nthe SG phase is stable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Mar 2009 14:25:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
